org.dellroad.muxable.simple

Class OutputQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dellroad.muxable.simple.OutputQueue

  • public class OutputQueue
extends Object
    A output queue of bytes stored in ByteBuffers.

    Instances are not thread safe.

      • enqueue

        public int enqueue(ByteBuffer data)
        Add the given data to queue.

        The caller must assume that this method takes "ownership" of data.

        Parameters:
        data - to enqueue
        Returns:
        some combination of the flags WAS_EMPTY, WAS_FULL, NOW_EMPTY, and/or NOW_FULL
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if data is null
